  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dad\u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dba \u0dc4\u0ddd \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d91\u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0d91\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The people of that country say that Gota should be given asylum or protection in the Maldives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the people of that country are currently urging the government of Maldives not to give shelter or asylum to the President Gotabaya Rajapaksa who left the country after leaving Sri Lanka in the worst crisis.",
        "A video of President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa being taken from Male under high security by the country's security forces is currently circulating on social media.",
        "Commenting on this video, the people of Maldives declare that Mr. Gotabaya Rajapaksa should not be granted asylum or protection in that country.",
        "They also state that the people of Maldives stand with the people of Sri Lanka."
      ],
